{
  "page": "Leona Woolfield",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Woodwright\" title=\"House Woodwright\"><img alt=\"House Woolfield.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/26/House_Woolfield.svg/50px-House_Woolfield.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/26/House_Woolfield.svg/75px-House_Woolfield.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/26/House_Woolfield.svg/100px-House_Woolfield.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Leona Woolfield</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Manderly\" title=\"House Manderly\"><img alt=\"House Manderly.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c9/House_Manderly.svg/50px-House_Manderly.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c9/House_Manderly.svg/75px-House_Manderly.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c9/House_Manderly.svg/100px-House_Manderly.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Wylis_%26_Leona_Manderly_by_Lopata_4.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Wylis &amp; Leona Manderly by Lopata 4.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f5/Wylis_%26_Leona_Manderly_by_Lopata_4.jpg/350px-Wylis_%26_Leona_Manderly_by_Lopata_4.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"403\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f5/Wylis_%26_Leona_Manderly_by_Lopata_4.jpg/525px-Wylis_%26_Leona_Manderly_by_Lopata_4.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f5/Wylis_%26_Leona_Manderly_by_Lopata_4.jpg/700px-Wylis_%26_Leona_Manderly_by_Lopata_4.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Leona and her husband <a href=\"/index.php/Wylis_Manderly\" title=\"Wylis Manderly\">Wylis Manderly</a> by Lopata 4</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Woolfield\" title=\"House Woolfield\">House Woolfield</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Manderly\" title=\"House Manderly\">House Manderly</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">Northmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nSer <a href=\"/index.php/Wylis_Manderly\" title=\"Wylis Manderly\">Wylis Manderly</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Wynafryd_Manderly\" title=\"Wynafryd Manderly\">Wynafryd Manderly</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Wylla_Manderly\" title=\"Wylla Manderly\">Wylla Manderly</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appears)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table> \n<p><b>Leona Woolfield</b> is a noblewoman of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Woolfield\" title=\"House Woolfield\">House Woolfield</a> and is the wife of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Wylis_Manderly\" title=\"Wylis Manderly\">Wylis Manderly</a>, the heir to <a href=\"/index.php/White_Harbor\" title=\"White Harbor\">White Harbor</a>. They have two daughters, <a href=\"/index.php/Wynafryd_Manderly\" title=\"Wynafryd Manderly\">Wynafryd</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Wylla_Manderly\" title=\"Wylla Manderly\">Wylla Manderly</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes_by_Leona\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes by Leona</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes_about_Leona\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes about Leona</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance\">Appearance</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leona_Woolfield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Leona is a plump pink woman with yellow hair, and her face is round, pink and fleshy.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> She follows the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leona_Woolfield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leona_Woolfield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lady Leona is present along with her daughters, <a href=\"/index.php/Wynafryd_Manderly\" title=\"Wynafryd Manderly\">Wynafryd</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Wylla_Manderly\" title=\"Wylla Manderly\">Wylla</a>, when Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Davos_Seaworth\" title=\"Davos Seaworth\">Davos Seaworth</a> attempts to persuade Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Wyman_Manderly\" title=\"Wyman Manderly\">Wyman Manderly</a> to support King <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a>. She insults Davos out of fear for her husband's safety—Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Wylis_Manderly\" title=\"Wylis Manderly\">Wylis</a> is a hostage of the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a>—fearing that if Wyman declares his support for Stannis her beloved husband will suffer for it. When Wylla refuses to stop demanding <a href=\"/index.php/House_Manderly\" title=\"House Manderly\">House Manderly</a>'s loyalty to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a> and that her grandfather Wyman should support Stannis, Leona drags her from the <a href=\"/index.php/Merman%27s_Court\" title=\"Merman&#39;s Court\">Merman's Court</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_by_Leona\">Quotes by Leona</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leona_Woolfield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes by Leona\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Davos</b>: I have a string of titles too. <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Rainwood\" title=\"Lord of the Rainwood\">Lord of the Rainwood</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Admiral_of_the_Narrow_Sea\" title=\"Admiral of the Narrow Sea\">Admiral of the Narrow Sea</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>.<br />\n<b>Leona</b>: <a href=\"/index.php/Admiral_of_the_Narrow_Sea\" title=\"Admiral of the Narrow Sea\">An admiral</a> without ships, <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">a hand</a> without fingers, in service to a king without <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">a throne</a>. Is this a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> who comes before us, or the answer to a child's riddle?<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Davos_Seaworth\" title=\"Davos Seaworth\">Davos Seaworth</a> and Leona</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Seven</a> defend <a href=\"/index.php/White_Harbor\" title=\"White Harbor\">White Harbor</a>. We do not fear <a href=\"/index.php/Melisandre\" title=\"Melisandre\">your red queen</a> or <a href=\"/index.php/R%27hllor\" title=\"R&#39;hllor\">her god</a>. Let her send what spells she will. The prayers of godly men will shield us against evil.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Leona to <a href=\"/index.php/Davos_Seaworth\" title=\"Davos Seaworth\">Davos Seaworth</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Young girls should be an ornament to the eye, not an ache in the ear.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Leona to <a href=\"/index.php/Wylla_Manderly\" title=\"Wylla Manderly\">Wylla Manderly</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_about_Leona\">Quotes about Leona</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leona_Woolfield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes about Leona\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>She speaks from fear. If <a href=\"/index.php/White_Harbor\" title=\"White Harbor\">White Harbor</a> should declare for <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Wylis_Manderly\" title=\"Wylis Manderly\">her husband</a> would answer with his life.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Davos_Seaworth\" title=\"Davos Seaworth\">Davos Seaworth</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Forgive her if you can, my lord. She is a foolish, frightened woman, and <a href=\"/index.php/Wylis_Manderly\" title=\"Wylis Manderly\">Wylis</a> is her life.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Wyman_Manderly\" title=\"Wyman Manderly\">Wyman Manderly</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Davos_Seaworth\" title=\"Davos Seaworth\">Davos Seaworth</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leona_Woolfield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"widt